*Subject:* MoU with Cooper Hospital





Dear All,







We are glad to inform you that a MoU has been  signed  between MPSTME,

NMIMS University and Hindu Hridaysamrat Balasaheb Thackeray Medical College

and Dr. R. N. Cooper Municipal General Hospital.



Understanding the need of collaborative/ Interdisciplinary research  in the

field of Medical and Engineering, the MoU will be helpful to our students

and  research scholars in the areas of-



1. Electrophysiological Signal Processing



2. Bio medical Image processing



3. Bioinformatics



4. Health informatics



5. Telemedicine



6. Medical Informatics



7. Technological enhancement in medical diagnosis



8. Hospital Management



9. Patient Management



10. Other areas of mutual agreement







This will be a good opportunity for you to undertake projects in the

healthcare domain. Kindly share with your students / scholars too,

encouraging them to make use of the opportunity.



We may also start joint certification programmes for Engineers and

healthcare professionals through this MoU.







*Appreciate the proactive involvement of Dr Avinash Tandle in initiating

and coordinating the process.  *







Warm Regards,



Alka Mahajan







DEAN, MPSTME, Mumbai

Greetings! NMIMS Mukesh Patel School of Technology Management & Engineering is delighted to bring to you the third edition of its Literature Fest, The Editorial Project.



We have some thrilling events with exciting prizes lined up. We are pleased to have Mr. Vivek Agnihotri, Ms. Shaheen Bhatt & Mr. Kumar Vishwas on board with us on day 1.



The artist that we present to you this time, is none other than Prateek Kuhad for our pro-night on day 2!



[image.png]

Popular for mesmerizing songs like Kho gaye ham kaha, cold/mess, Kasoor, Dil Beparwah, Tune Kaha, & many others, Prateek will be entertaining us all with his ephonious voice & melodious tunes.
